data.title: Home
data.text:
Eastern Section vs Southeast Section

Southeast 5, East 4

Northern Section vs Western Section

The West All-Stars outlasted the North All-Stars 15-12 at a packed Sauk City ball park Friday.

Jake Zeal (Shullsburg/Benton Fever) had a solo home run for the West in the second. Jameson Johnson (Blanchardville Bullets) was 2x3 with a double and Josh Cartwright (Muscoda Mudcats) had two singles in four trips.

Sean Reilly (Dodgeville Knights), Ayden Halverson (Ridgeway Cardinals), Tanner Johnson, (Argyle Beavers), Trey Gordon (Hollandale Rockies), Cade Janecke (Wiota Indians) and Mason Atkins (Muscoda Mudcats) all had solo hits for the West.

Tanler Ames (Hollandale Rockies) pitched two scoreless innings for the West. Eli Zimmerman (Argyle Beavers) pitched one.
